{"tid":1677459,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GD退伍敬禮姿勢遭批評！ 「手指沒併攏上下抖」粉絲貼照平反…韓網吵成一團","createTime":"2019-10-27T06:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T06:25:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc3374f05a1a9c3718b402796594e03e50f5897","tid":1677459,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3461666/org/17e989a311a542e0bfbf347b4d15a244.jpg/bsseDY8OW6Ea3hJUZ9YnPPB-mUvFom8NZ0K0lmdCtJY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3461666%2Forg%2F17e989a311a542e0bfbf347b4d15a244.jpg%2FbsseDY8OW6Ea3hJUZ9YnPPB-mUvFom8NZ0K0lmdCtJY&h=62b12ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓星GD（G-Dragon、權志龍）26日正式退伍，特別和媽媽一起準備麵包給到場粉絲外，也特別拿著大聲公表達感謝之意，不過接受媒體訪問時擺出的敬禮引起韓網議論紛紛。<br />\n<br />\nGD於26日一早正式退伍，面對來迎接的3000粉絲表達感謝心意外，也特別和媽媽一起準備好餐點要給等待許久的粉絲：「大家吃早餐了嗎？要吃才行啊！」接受媒體訪問時看出來有些生澀緊張，原本說完感言要離開，被經紀人拉回擺敬禮姿勢拍照，但彎曲的手指和原本應該正對著眉尾的手隨著次數漸漸下降。<br />\n<br />\n照片和新聞曝光後引起韓網熱議，「老實說連我不太清楚姿勢的人看都覺得怪怪的」、「因為退伍了就隨便敬禮了嗎」，另一部分網友則貼出照片幫忙平反，「這是退伍前GD和同期、後輩一起照的，請不要隨意寫下批評」、「針對人家敬禮姿勢說嘴真的滿誇張的，就算是軍中幹部也有很多人敬禮姿勢都很奇怪的」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4466/4466152.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4466%2F4466152.jpg&h=41a31fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼韓網反應。（圖／翻攝自PANN）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4466/4466153.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4466%2F4466153.jpg&h=8d091f30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fb1b49e51d7214652e6aa61522862ba29101255","tid":1677459,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446c064f5389a85eb93938b4e28578eea82fecc7","tid":1677459,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"屌到冇嘢好屌"},{"pid":"70ecf0c18f347938461c77a171794fd98fb7bad0","tid":1677459,"uid":266010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"三點<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/un9HRVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fun9HRVA.jpg&h=73f2e7db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jb22RVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjb22RVB.jpg&h=3afe7f20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TB7m7tW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTB7m7tW.jpg&h=35ba214d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3aWnRVC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3aWnRVC.jpg&h=00967356&s={SIZE}\" />梳士巴利花園等你"},{"pid":"2c14a7be0c21c1f4c4094d05f3081c1dc3f25ffe","tid":1677459,"uid":28730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"Eye4HK"},{"pid":"7722b53f320f1054e6f71a163ba502604310ea54","tid":1677459,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c14a7be0c21c1f4c4094d05f3081c1dc3f25ffe","tid":1677459,"uid":28730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"Eye4HK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"仲有個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8c53f53bbe1aa5da2ee863bce71cd4a12fde15","tid":1677459,"uid":242009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"蒙面+ 還眼姐<br />\n我就覺得一啲都唔怪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}